						               													<description>Ignacy Lukasiewicz has just invented a way to convert oil into kerosene. The black gold fever begins in Galicia. With little capital, one begins to invest in oil parcels, build oil wells, merge into companies and try to be more successful than the competition.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The way to success is to invest in technology, because with inventions you can get ahead of your opponents. The one of you who has the most parcels, cash and patents for inventions at the end of the game will win. Are you ready to follow in the footsteps of Ignacy Lukasiewicz?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#197;&amp;#129;ukasiewicz: Nafta i Gaz is a game for 2 to 5 players aged 12 or higher, which enables us to recreate the early days of the oil extraction in Galicia. Players incarnate entrepreneurs, who will compete for land, contracts and inventions. The most resourceful will emerge victorious.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
